{"article_id":"Ntcm9ruLBp92Itmh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Billionaire businessman Michael Bloomberg ended weeks of speculation","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"- marked by a stunning mea culpa for his past defense of ' stop and frisk ' -","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and formally declared himself a Democratic candidate for the White House on Sunday .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"The media mogul , New York City ' s last three-term mayor , declared to supporters in a launch video and statement ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"\" I ' m running for president","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to defeat Donald Trump","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and rebuild America .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"We can not afford four more years of President Trump ' s reckless and unethical actions . \"","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" He represents an existential threat to our country and our values .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"If he wins another term in office ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"we may never recover from the damage .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"The stakes could not be higher .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"We must win this election .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"And we must begin rebuilding America .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"I believe","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"my unique set of experiences in business , government , and philanthropy will enable me to win","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"and lead , \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"said Bloomberg ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"who had ruled out a presidential run as recently as March .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"He faces a tough fight","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to win the nomination over top tier Democratic candidates like former Vice President Joe Biden and Sens . Elizabeth Warren and Bernie Sanders","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"who have been campaigning for months ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"including five debates .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"But Biden ' s debate stumbles","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"coupled with the unexpected strength of the twin far-left candidacies of Warren and Sanders","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"left Bloomberg and his advisors worried","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Democrats could select a nominee","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"unable to beat President Trump next fall ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"sources told The Post .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"His advisors believe","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the mogul ' s $ 52 billion fortune and willingness","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"to self-fund","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"means he can catapult himself into contention .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"The ad","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"released online","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and airing in key battleground states","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"starting Sunday","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"is part of the three-term New York mayor ' s $ 34 million initial ad campaign","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"announcing his candidacy .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" He could have just been the middle-class kid","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"who made good","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"but Mike Bloomberg became the guy","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"who did good , \"","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"said a tweet","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"linking to the video with the logo Mike Bloomberg 2020 .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"\" After building a business","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that created thousands of jobs ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"he took charge of a city","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"still reeling from 9/11 .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"A three-term mayor","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"who helped bring it back from the ashes ,","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"bringing jobs and thousands of affordable housing units with it . \"","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"He also trumpeted his work","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"advocating for gun control measures and efforts","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"to fight climate change .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"It said","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"the 77-year-old will \" restore faith in the dream","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that defines us","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"where the wealthy will pay more in taxes","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"and the middle class get their fair share .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Everyone","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"without health insurance can get it ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and everyone","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"who likes theirs ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"keep it . \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Bloomberg ' s official declaration follows two stunning reversals","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"- and apologies -","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"from the famously stubborn politician","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"as he plotted his entry into the race .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"The first came","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"when he apologized for sexist remarks","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"he made","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"while leading his eponymous Midtown media empire through a spokesman .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"see also Bloomberg apologizes for controversial stop-and-frisk policy","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Former mayor Michael Bloomberg offered a stunning apology on Sunday ...","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"His second ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"made in person last Sunday ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"stunned the city","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"- reversing his decade of unquestioned public support for the NYPD ' s controversial ' stop-and-frisk ' policy","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"that was ruled unconstitutional","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"and fueled a political backlash","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"that elected his successor , Mayor de Blasio .","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"Political experts said","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"Bloomberg had to make the move","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"to square his politics with the shifting debate across the country","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"- and in the Democratic Party -","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"over criminal justice and policing .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" Why did he do it ?","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Bloomberg knows","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"to compete for the nomination","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"he has to get a chunk of the African-American vote , \"","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"University of Virginia political science professor Larry Sabato told The Post .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"\" It ' s that simple .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"If you can ' t compete for the black vote","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"you might as well save your money . \"","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"He added :","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"\" You ' ve got to stop people from booing you .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"He wants to say ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"` I apologize for that","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"but this is what I did for the African-American community . \"","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"That wasn ' t Bloomberg ' s only political maneuvering in the run-up to Sunday ' s announcement .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"He nabbed ballot spots in two states with early registration deadlines , Alabama and Arkansas .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"The online advertisements","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Bloomberg is funding","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"target four states","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"expected to be hotly contested during the 2020 election :","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Arizona , Michigan , Pennsylvania and Wisconsin .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"see also Michael Bloomberg more disliked than any Democratic candidate :","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"poll","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"Michael Bloomberg would face a tough start to his presidential ...","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"On his campaign ' s website Sunday , the billionaire Bloomberg highlighted an economy","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"that is \" tilted against most Americans ,","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"\" a health care system","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"that \" costs too much","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"and doesn ' t cover everyone ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"\" communities \" ravaged by gun violence , \" and a global climate crisis","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"that is \" growing worse by the day . \"","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Bloomberg also described a \" cruel and dysfunctional \" immigration system , schools","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that are failing students in an \" increasingly high-tech world ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and special interest groups","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"that \" corrupt \" Washington","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"and \" block progress on all of these issues . \"","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Then","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"addressing Trump by name ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"he challenged the president on gun violence","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"and \" won stronger gun laws in states across the country \"","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"and \" took on Trump the climate denier . \"","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"\" I know what it takes to beat Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"because I already have .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"And I will do it again.","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"I ' ve never shied away from a tough fight , \"","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"he said on the campaign site .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"\" Defeating Trump","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"- and rebuilding America -","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"is the most urgent and important fight of our lives .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"And I ' m going all in . \"","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Bloomberg recounted","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"how his father never earned more than $ 6,000 in a year ,","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"and how his parents instilled in him and his sister the need for an education .","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"He also reflects on being laid off at 39","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"and coming up with an idea","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"to start a company -","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"\" so I took a chance . \"","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"\" Today our company employs 20,000 people","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"and generates large profits ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"almost all of which go to helping people across the country and around the world .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"I ' ve always believed in investing in our employees","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"and treating them well .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"We pay employees very well","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"and provide the best health care benefits","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"money can buy .","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"And","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"if someone has a baby ,","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"they get six months of paid leave , \"","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"noting","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"how he was elected mayor of New York weeks after the Sept. 11 terror attacks ,","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"he wrote :","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"\" It was a frightening time for our city and country .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"But we rebuilt the economy with new jobs and opportunity","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"- for people on all rungs of the economic ladder. \"","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"Bloomberg has said","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"the Sunday ad rollout will be part of a $ 100 million online ad campaign","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"targeting President Trump .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"They are expected to run through the primary season ,","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"regardless of Bloomberg ' s personal political fortunes ,","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"aides told The Post .","depth":7},{"id":170,"text":"Trump won all of the states in 2016 ,","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"but public opinion polls have shown","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"that he is vulnerable","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"as the 2020 election shapes up .","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"Bloomberg earned plaudits from Democrats","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"for pumping millions into the 2018 midterm elections","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"to help the party ' s candidates across the country .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"The crowded field of Democrats","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"vying for president","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"has largely been focused on the primary contest .","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"Some Democratic leaders are growing increasingly concerned","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"that a nasty primary fight","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"won by the party ' s progressive and liberal wings","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"could give Trump a chance","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"to gain ground in during the spring and summer .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"The president ' s reelection campaign has started spending heavily on online advertising ,","depth":2},{"id":186,"text":"using the war chest","depth":4},{"id":187,"text":"he has already begun to amass","depth":4},{"id":188,"text":"to target general election voters .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":377,"left":373,"right":376,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":373,"left":253,"right":372,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":191,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":190,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":206,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":195,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":3,"right":194,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":193,"right":7,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":4,"right":192,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{